Description: Drop Smart Scopes Search functionality and remove libsoup* dependencies.
 Smart Scopes Search functionality has been broken for many years already and
 it could be dropped. In future Unity will have similar feature implemented but
 without 3rd-party servers working as data aggregators or fetchers.

 This patch also removes all dependencies on libsoup* libraries including
 obsolete libsoup-gnome-2.4-1 (LP: #2069962).
Author: Tomasz Jeruzalski <tomekdev17@gmail.com>
Bug: https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/unity-scope-home/+bug/2069962
Last-Update: 2026-02-16
